oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Steve Wariner Publicity Photo
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Wariner, Steve;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white head-and-shoulders studio portrait of Steve Wariner. The photo was released by MCA Records Nashville. On the back of the photo, a handwritten note says, "3 L-R 3 1/2 TB," presumably in reference to the size of the metal photoplate made from the photo.
